name: Stop in the name of love
description:

In today's world, machines and men begin to compete for the earth, the two universes begin to be indistinguishable, so that we humans must prove to other machines that we are alive and feel emotions. have to prove to other machines to be alive and feel emotions. The word robot comes from Czech and means slave, once upon a time this was enough to divide the two races, today it is no longer enough.
